n: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Acceso a la configuración de inventario del producto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:42.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El sistema muestra los campos &quot;Stock Mínimo&quot; y &quot;Stock Máximo&quot;. El usuario ingresa los valores correspondientes y confirma la operación. El sistema válida la información y registra los límites de stock asociados al producto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:52.896484375pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: El usuario ingresa un valor negativo o no numérico. El sistema muestra un mensaje de error y solicita corregir la información.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Excepción 2: El valor de stock máximo es menor que en valor de stock mínimo. El sistema muestra un mensaje de error y no permite guardar la configuración.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:36pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Los valores de stock mínimo y máximo quedan asociados al producto para su utilización en la gestión de inventario y generación de alertas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="490" width="580" x="-490" y="1630" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
